  "texts": [
    "The \"images\" variable has a shape of (1460, 16, 768, 1152), representing 1460 images with 16 channels, a length of 768, and a width of 1152.",
    "On the other hand, the \"boxes\" variable has a shape of (1460, 15, 5), signifying 1460 images with 15 ground-truth boxes per image.",
    "The 5 coordinates in each box correspond to x_min, x_max, y_min, y_max, and the associated class label.",
    "Table 1 provides a detailed mapping of the class labels for four cyclone classes.",
    "For Cyclone detection, the study focused on seven face (T500), (d) Zonal wind at 850 mbar pressure surface (U850), (e) Meridional wind at 850 mbar pressure surface (V850), (f) Z100, and (g) Geopotential Z at 200 mbar pressure surface (Z200)"
  ]
}